{"tid":213583,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[避孕套]曼聯宣布拒絕與伊巴謙莫域續約，但會負責日後治癒","createTime":"2017-04-23T08:34:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-24T14:49:29.000Z","uid":54373,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"27af85ae26b7d98db1439d9262cc8bb9547e42a4","tid":213583,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:34:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 魚拉特<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"08ecd943ed5e231bcda6c6e869c6bf21359aa415","tid":213583,"uid":78072,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:35:21.000Z","msg":"曼聯<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"70e4691983ceb59a44172dbf3b78271134104a8f","tid":213583,"uid":19552,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:35:51.000Z","msg":"醫好都廢晒武功..."},{"pid":"9be65cefbc70388c4d8cea8deb833135daf83dc7","tid":213583,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:36:38.000Z","msg":"由於喺對陣安德列治既比賽入面受傷，令到瑞典前鋒伊巴謙莫域需要接受至少9個月既休戰，而值得一提既係，「呂布」同曼聯既合約將會喺今季完結之後到期，而一直好希望完成續約既紅魔，喺態度上似乎出現180度既轉變。<br />\n<br />\n英國《鏡報》報導，曼聯決定唔會再同伊巴謙莫域續約，因為呢位前聖日耳門球員已經35歲，喺傷愈歸來之後都未必可以重拾勇態，再加上續約完成之後，意味住紅魔要一直出糧俾高人工既伊巴，而喺經濟既角度上去諗，續約絕對唔係一個有益既行為。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯都唔會對伊巴用完即棄既，有消息人士透露，紅魔會喺「呂布」好返之前，為呢位瑞典老將繼續提供醫療援助，總算係對伊巴既最後一點心意。</span></span>"},{"pid":"d0e338c702863ecdbf63511e13c5d7da8393c622","tid":213583,"uid":12736,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T08:37:08.000Z","msg":"鏡報"},{"pid":"47e57dea241d43d9b740e4b41bed1b2f6ffc574b","tid":213583,"uid":31666,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:44:07.000Z","msg":"God of Manchester <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/39.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d7bb1bfaa8a0d4079c142c4d6c44b7c2c4d66ba1","tid":213583,"uid":8968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:51:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>鏡報</blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cdb22b2f650061f22e47db87ba6506d197f8fdcc","tid":213583,"uid":38456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:52:19.000Z","msg":"source?"},{"pid":"d7f50c83ef8fcc8fd3af2b471c89218f78caa7f8","tid":213583,"uid":52876,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T09:59:12.000Z","msg":"I came like a god left like a condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2fe866dfb874861224597211d2bfd2e469564393","tid":213583,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-23T11:36:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b433ed8b64ccd0e4544a74a37e8e8510e25f7de","tid":213583,"uid":96741,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-27T22:44:43.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>由於喺對陣安德列治既比賽入面受傷，令到瑞典前鋒伊巴謙莫域需要接受至少9個月既休戰，而值得一提既係，「呂布」同曼聯既合約將會喺今季完結之後到期，而一直好希望完成續約既紅魔，喺態度上似乎出現180度既轉變。<br />\n<br />\n英國《鏡報》報導，曼聯決定唔會再同伊巴謙莫域續約，因為呢位前聖日耳門球員已經35歲，喺傷愈歸來之後都未必可以重拾勇態，再加上續約完成之後，意味住紅魔要一直出糧俾高人工既伊巴，而喺經濟既角度上去諗，續約絕對唔係一個有益既行為。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n不過，<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">曼聯都唔會對伊巴用完即棄既，有消息人士透露，紅魔會喺「呂布」好返之前，為呢位瑞典老將繼續提供醫療援助，總算係對伊巴既最後一點心意。</span></span></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n期待到時在曼聯醫好再, 季中再自由身轉去競爭對手, 攞完冠軍後立即去MLS  ,無仇報"},{"pid":"53294a769d37f7e91a5037983fb36cff7d67dc94","tid":213583,"uid":18959,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-28T00:21:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>I came like a god left like a condom<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3